    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-04-03T08:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-04-03T08:00:00-05:00" n="443"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d443">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 EW/4–348: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The United States Political Adviser for Germany</hi>
                        (<persName corresp="#p_MRD1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Murphy</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">urgent</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-04-03T14:00:00+01:00"
                            >April 3, 1948—2 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">no distribution</hi>
                </p>
                <p>774. All non-cultural restitution to USSR and satellites stopped effective
                    yesterday. Restitutions Branch instructed hold all released property not already
                    shipped, not to publicize this move and to stall off restitutions missions with
                    any excuse.</p>
                <p>List restitutions property released or shipped Hungary (re <gloss
                        target="#t_mytel1">mytel</gloss>s 751 and 752, April 1<note n="1"
                        xml:id="d443fn1">Neither printed.</note>) should not be publicized.</p>
                <p>Cultural restitution and restitution to west to continue normally.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_MRD1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Murphy</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
